        "code": "<section class=\"rcp-quicklinks\" aria-label=\"Quick links\">\n  <nav class=\"rcp-ql-nav\">\n    <ul class=\"rcp-ql-line\">\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-half-tights\">Golf Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-split-shorts\">Golf Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-golf posters\">Golf Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-shirts\">Golf Shirts</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/lifestyle-clothing\">Graphic Shirts</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/lifestyle-clothing\">Hoodies</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-posters\">Posters</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/collections/golf-stickers\">Stickers</a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </nav>\n</section>\n<style>\n  .rcp-quicklinks { background: #fff; padding: 10px 0; }\n  .rcp-ql-nav { max-width: 3000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 10px; }\n  .rcp-ql-line {\n    list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-wrap: nowrap;\n    gap: 8px; justify-content: center; align-items: center; overflow: auto; scrollbar-width: none;\n  }\n  .rcp-ql-line::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n  .rcp-ql-line a {\n    display: inline-block; min-width: 140px; padding: 10px 20px;\n    border: 2px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none;\n    text-align: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n    text-transform: uppercase; color: #333; background: #fff;\n    font-family: 'Montserrat', var(--BTN-FONT-STACK);\n    transition: all 0.2s ease;\n  }\n  .rcp-ql-line a:hover, .rcp-ql-line a:active { background: #2E7D32; color: #fff; border-color: #2E7D32; }\n  .rcp-ql-line a:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid #2E7D32; outline-offset: 2px; }\n  @media (max-width: 763px) {\n    .rcp-ql-line { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; gap: 6px; overflow: visible; }\n    .rcp-ql-line a { width: 100%; }\n  }\n</style>",
